{"word":"ἄμυστις","slug":"ἄμυστις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄμυστις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀμυστί'><el>ἀμυστί</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a long draught</i>, <b><a href='S:Anacreon Lyricus'>Anacr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>deep drinking, tippling</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a large cup</i>, used by the Thracians, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}